ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 213, Newfoundland and Labrador
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 213 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of NEWFOUNDLAND and LABRADOR, with respect to the extreme flooding and mudslides that occurred in Newfoundland and Labrador from January 12 to 14, 2018.
